                            <comment id="17772423" author="tilman" created="Fri, 6 Oct 2023 03:26:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There is a log output:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; Info  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;TilingPaint&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Pattern surface is too large, will be clipped&lt;br/&gt;
 Info  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;TilingPaint&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; width: 6857.7163, height: -3946.014&lt;br/&gt;
 Info  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;TilingPaint&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; XStep: 4913.0, YStep: 2827.0&lt;br/&gt;
 Info  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;TilingPaint&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; bbox: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;-4138.3696,-1024.1337,774.6304,1802.8663&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 Info  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;TilingPaint&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; pattern matrix: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1.3958308,0.0,0.0,-1.3958309,-4.8828125E-4,1080.0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 Info  &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;TilingPaint&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; concatenated matrix: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1.3958308,0.0,0.0,-1.3958309,-4.8828125E-4,1080.0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Try setting the pdfbox.rendering.tilingpaint.maxedge property to 7000 and it works. However you&apos;ll need more memory. There is a huge image in that file used for this pattern of which only a small part is actually used.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
